<html>
<body>
<p>Reports unresolved references and invalid Thymeleaf expressions.</p>

<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
<pre><code lang="html">
&lt;html xmlns:th="https://www.thymeleaf.org"&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;form th:object="${<strong>unknownPet</strong>}"  &lt;!-- Cannot resolve 'unknownPet'  --&gt;
        class="form-horizontal" method="post"&gt;
    &lt;input type="hidden" name="id" th:value="*{<strong>id</strong>}" /&gt; &lt;!-- Cannot resolve 'id'  --&gt;
  &lt;/form&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>